          type="button"
          class="btn-close"
          data-bs-dismiss="modal"
          aria-label="Close"
        ></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        23/06/2021 - Added Login and Sign up functionality as well as database
        which allows you to save your own watchlist in your own database.
        <hr />
        02/06/2021 - This web application is constantly updated. For legal
        purposes, I have refrained from scraping videos.
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
